69. How do you protect routes based on roles (RBAC)?
70. How do you optimize Angular for Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID)?
71. How do you integrate Angular with WebSockets?
72. How do you design a multi-step form wizard?
73. How do you handle errors in RxJS pipelines?
74. How do you lazy load modules and components?
75. How do you implement component-level caching?

